---
// Archivo: src/components/home/Services.astro
---
<section class="flex bg-[url(/ruido.png)] bg-no-repeat bg-cover justify-center pb-24 relative z-10" id="servicios">
  <div class="border-t border-gray-600 w-11/12 mx-auto mt-24 text-tertiary">
    
    <div class="flex justify-between py-4 mb-16 border-b border-gray-800">
      <p class="text-quaternary uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">áreas de acción *</p>
      <p><span class="text-quaternary">03</span> // 05</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-gray-800 mb-12">
      
      <div class="group hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all duration-500 p-8 md:p-12 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-gray-800 relative">
        <span class="parrafe text-xs uppercase tracking-widest border border-current px-3 py-1 mb-8 inline-block">Sistemas // UTN</span>
        <h3 class="title text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-6 uppercase text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">
          Ingeniería <br> de Software
        </h3>
        <p class="parrafe text-base text-gray-400 group-hover:text-gray-800 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Infraestructuras web escalables y código eficiente. Desde el diseño de la interfaz hasta la base de datos relacional.
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-gray-800 group-hover:border-gray-300 pt-6">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            <span class="text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">/01</span> Web a Medida (Front & Back)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            <span class="text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">/02</span> Sistemas de Gestión (CRUDs)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            <span class="text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">/03</span> Asesoría en Hardware & Rendimiento
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="group hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all duration-500 p-8 md:p-12 relative">
        <span class="parrafe text-xs uppercase tracking-widest border border-current px-3 py-1 mb-8 inline-block">Espacio // UBA</span>
        <h3 class="title text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-6 uppercase text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">
          Arquitectura <br> Visual
        </h3>
        <p class="parrafe text-base text-gray-400 group-hover:text-gray-800 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Traducción de planimetrías a realidades virtuales inmersivas. Rigor espacial, iluminación física y texturizado.
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-gray-800 group-hover:border-gray-300 pt-6">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            <span class="text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">/01</span> Renders Fotorrealistas & CGI
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            <span class="text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">/02</span> Modelado 3D de alta precisión
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            <span class="text-quaternary group-hover:text-black">/03</span> Postproducción Gráfica (Adobe Suite)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-end">
      <a 
        href="/servicios" 
        class="parrafe text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-black bg-quaternary px-8 py-4 hover:bg-white hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 font-bold"
      >
        Ver alcance y stack tecnológico →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>